# DevBox Commands

DevBox provides a comprehensive set of commands organized into three main categories:

## Service Management

Commands for controlling your services' lifecycle:

- `up` - Start services
- `down` - Stop services
- `restart` - Restart services
- `ps` - View running processes
- `logs` - View service logs

## Project Operations

Commands for managing your DevBox projects:

- `list` - List all projects
- `info` - View project details
- `update` - Update project configuration and sources
- `destroy` - Remove a project

## Development Commands

Commands for day-to-day development:

- `run` - Execute commands in services
- `shell` - Get interactive shell access

For detailed information about each command, please refer to their respective documentation pages. 